程序包 models

类 GoogleAPI

  • java.lang.Object
    • models.GoogleAPI
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    GoogleAPIInterface
    public class GoogleAPI
extends java.lang.Object
implements GoogleAPIInterface
    This is API interface calling class that handles requests from controllers. All the API calling methods are defined and implemented here. API calling model is separated from other local date processing logic.
    作者:
    Yuxuan Luan, Rui Li, Junwei Zhang
